* Proper Orthogonal Decompositon (Snapshot POD) Code
* Description

Follows the paper by [[https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/journal-of-fluid-mechanics/article/abs/reconstruction-of-the-global-velocity-field-in-the-axisymmetric-mixing-layer-utilizing-the-proper-orthogonal-decomposition/68BAA266FC58F299B2D9DA612C8F4A6C][Citrini and George 2000]]

$$\lim _{\tau \rightarrow \infty} \frac{1}{\tau} \int_{0}^{\tau} r^{1 / 2} \boldsymbol{u}(m ; r, t) \alpha_{n}^{*}(m ; t) \mathrm{d} t=\Phi_{n}(m ; r) \lambda^{n}(m)$$
